                <strong><a href="https://idp.cpp.edu/idp/profile/cas/login?service=https://cmsweb.cpp.edu/psp/HPOMPRDF/EMPLOYEE/HRMS/c/SA_LEARNER_SERVICES.SSS_STUDENT_CENTER.GBL?pslnkid=POM_BD_STDNT_SC&amp;amp;FolderPath=PORTAL_ROOT_OBJECT.POM_BD_SS.POM_BD_STDNT.POM_BD_STDNT_SC&amp;amp;IsFolder=false&amp;amp;IgnoreParamTempl=FolderPath%2cIsFolder?cmd=start&amp;amp;amp;languageCd=ENG&amp;amp;amp;userid=PS&amp;amp;amp;pwd=z&amp;amp;amp;calstateEduPersonEmplID" style="text-align:left; vertical-align:bottom" target="_blank" title="">Student Center<span class="fa fa-long-arrow-right fa-lg" style="padding-left: 10px;"></span></a></strong>
                <br />
                <div class="well well-sm blurb">
                    In the student center, you can view holds, search and register for classes, view to dos, view/update personal information, view/pay fees, and view/accept/decline aid.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
